    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Manipal Digital Health Holdings Services. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Full Stack Developer to strengthen our Delhi-based team.\n\nAbout Manipal Digital Health Holdings Services:\nManipal Digital Health Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Manipal Digital Health Holdings Services!",
